body:
Ignore this if you want

OkAy, so I know subscribers aren’t what make you a good YouTuber, but someone tell me why DnP are loosing an average of around 50-100, subs each day since the hiatus… It’s been only a day that I’ve kept exact track, but I know they’ve lost from 50-100 each day…

Phil yesterday: 4,182,253

Phil today: 4,182,187

Dan yesterday: 6,488,518

Dan today: 6,488,341

DnPG yesterday: 3,120,362

DnPG today: 3,120,252

I’m not trying to be rude or inconsiderate, and I don’t want to just point out the bad. Because there are many reasons they could be loosing subscribers, but for them to start dropping so quickly recently… it’s a little suspicious.

Sorry for this, I just wanted to rant to someone/something besides the few friends I have…
